*Će* biti lepo vreme tokom celog vikenda. (It will be nice weather throughout the whole weekend.)

Danas *ću* biti na odmoru. (Today I will be on vacation.)

Neću imati vremena za izlaske. (I won't have time for outings.)

*Ćemo* se videti u nedelju. (We will see each other on Sunday.)

*Ćale* je poklanjao mojoj sestri novu haljinu. (My father gave my sister a new dress.)